wikibasecirrus-desc: Wikibase extension for using CirrusSearch functionality
wikibasecirrus-inlabel-unknown-language-: inlabel keyword contains unknown language code: $1
wikibasecirrus-inlabel-too-many-language: inlabel keyword provided too many language codes. Searching $1 of the $2 provided languages
wikibasecirrus-inlabel-no-query-provided: inlabel keyword was provided an empty search string
wikibasecirrus-rescore-profile-prefix: Default rescore profile for completion search
wikibasecirrus-rescore-profile-prefix-bo: Rescore profile for completion search with statement boosting
wikibasecirrus-rescore-profile-fulltext: Default rescore profile for fulltext search
wikibasecirrus-rescore-profile-fulltext-: Rescore profile for fulltext search with phrase scoring
wikibasecirrus-search-namespace-mix: Mixing entity and article namespaces in search is currently not supported. Only entity namespaces will be searched.
wikibasecirrus-haswbstatement-feature-no: haswbstatement keyword contains no valid statements
